OL,5,Cwater
OL,7,FSouth West Water has warned customers
OL,8,Fover reports of scam calls targeting
OL,9,Fthose affected by contaminated water
OL,10,Fin the Brixham area of Devon.
OL,12,FThousands of households were told not
OL,13,Fto drink their tap water without
OL,14,Fboiling it last week, .
OL,16,FThose impacted have been offered
OL,17,Ffinancial compensation - but now the
OL,18,Fwater company has said it has heard
OL,19,Fthat some of them are receiving scam
OL,20,Fcalls by fraudsters trying to obtain
OL,21,Ftheir bank details.
