OL,7,FIn a post on X, South West Water
OL,8,Fwrote: "We have been made aware of
OL,9,Fscam calls to customers, claiming to
OL,10,Fbe from South West Water, in relation
OL,11,Fto your direct debit details and a
OL,12,Fcompensation claim.
OL,14,F"It is important to reiterate that we
OL,15,Fdo not need to contact you and you do
OL,16,Fnot need to do anything."
OL,18,FThe company has said that payments
OL,19,Fwill be made automatically and that no
OL,20,Ffinancial details need to be passed on.
