OL,7,FThey added: "For all household
OL,8,Fcustomers who have been issued with
OL,9,Fthe Boil Water Notice you will receive
OL,10,Fyour compensation by way of an
OL,11,Fautomatic payment. For business
OL,12,Fcustomers, this payment will be made
OL,13,Fvia your Retailer.
OL,15,F"Where we hold direct debit details
OL,16,Fthis will be made as an immediate
OL,17,Fpayment, where we do not this will be
OL,18,Fadded as a credit to the next
OL,19,Favailable bill."
