OL,7,FSouth West Water initially offered
OL,8,Fcustomers #15 in compensation for the
OL,9,Fdisruption, which has seen thousands
OL,10,Fof customers forced to collect bottles
OL,11,Fof drinking water and boil their tap
OL,12,Fwater. But this was then raised to
OL,13,F#115, following criticism.
OL,15,FOn Saturday 18 May, this was then
OL,16,Fincreased again for the remaining
OL,17,Fhouseholds to #215.
