OL,7,FSouth West Water has said anyone who
OL,8,Freceives a scam call should not give
OL,9,Fout any bank details, hang up and
OL,10,Freport it to Action Fraud.
OL,12,FIt added that if anyone has any
OL,13,Fdoubts, customers can call them on
OL,14,F0344 346 1010.
